                    <textarea class="text_field" style="width: 100%; display: none;" rows="27" id="page_content_text" title="TYPE FULL PAGE CONTENT HERE" placeholder="TYPE FULL PAGE CONTENT HERE" aria-hidden="true">&lt;h2&gt;Tips for traveling in the summer season.&lt;/h2&gt;
                                &lt;p&gt;1. Choose your destination wisely: Consider the weather conditions and temperature of your destination. Places near the coast, mountains, or lakes can offer cooler temperatures compared to cities or deserts.&lt;/p&gt;
                                &lt;p&gt;2. Pack light: Summer clothes are usually lightweight and easy to pack. Bring comfortable shoes, a hat, sunglasses, and sunscreen to protect yourself from the sun.&lt;/p&gt;
                                &lt;p&gt;3. Plan outdoor activities: Take advantage of the longer days and plan outdoor activities such as hiking, swimming, or kayaking. Don't forget to bring a water bottle to stay hydrated.&lt;/p&gt;
                                &lt;p&gt;4. Avoid peak travel times: Summer is a popular time for travel, so try to avoid peak travel times to save money and avoid crowds. Consider traveling mid-week or early in the morning.&lt;/p&gt;
                                &lt;p&gt;5. Be flexible: Summer weather can be unpredictable, so be flexible with your plans. Have a backup plan if your outdoor activities get rained out.&lt;/p&gt;
                                &lt;p&gt;6. Stay safe: Stay hydrated, wear sunscreen, and be aware of your surroundings when traveling in the summer season. Keep an eye on weather alerts and be prepared for any emergencies.&lt;/p&gt;
                                &lt;p&gt;Call us at &lt;span style="color: #3598db;"&gt;&lt;a style="color: #3598db;" title="Call Us" href="tel:+1(415)%20494-4044"&gt;+1(415) 494-4044&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; for your &lt;span style="color: #3598db;"&gt;&lt;a style="color: #3598db;" title="Airport Transportation Service" href="../../services/airport-transfer/"&gt;airport transportation&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; or &lt;span style="color: #3598db;"&gt;&lt;a style="color: #3598db;" title="Book Online" href="../../online-booking/"&gt;book online&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</textarea><div role="application" class="tox tox-tinymce tox-platform-touch" style="visibility: hidden; width: 100%; height: 411px;"><div class="tox-editor-container"><div class="tox-editor-header"><div role="menubar" data-alloy-tabstop="true" class="tox-menubar"><button aria-haspopup="true" role="menuitem" type="button" data-alloy-tabstop="true" unselectable="on" tabindex="-1" class="tox-mbtn tox-mbtn--select" aria-expanded="false" style="user-select: none;"><span class="tox-mbtn__select-label">File</span><div class="tox-mbtn__select-chevron"><svg width="10" height="10"><path d="M8.7 2.2c.3-.3.8-.3 1 0 .4.4.4.9 0 1.2L5.7 7.8c-.3.3-.9.3-1.2 0L.2 3.4a.8.8 0 0 1 0-1.2c.3-.3.8-.3 1.1 0L5 6l3.7-3.8z" fill-rule="nonzero"></path></svg></div></button><button aria-haspopup="true" role="menuitem" type="button" data-alloy-tabstop="true" unselectable="on" tabindex="-1" class="tox-mbtn tox-mbtn--select" aria-expanded="false" style="user-select: none;"><span class="tox-mbtn__select-label">Edit</span><div class="tox-mbtn__select-chevron"><svg width="10" height="10"><path d="M8.7 2.2c.3-.3.8-.3 1 0 .4.4.4.9 0 1.2L5.7 7.8c-.3.3-.9.3-1.2 0L.2 3.4a.8.8 0 0 1 0-1.2c.3-.3.8-.3 1.1 0L5 6l3.7-3.8z" fill-rule="nonzero"></path></svg></div></button><button aria-haspopup="true" role="menuitem" type="button" data-alloy-tabstop="true" unselectable="on" tabindex="-1" class="tox-mbtn tox-mbtn--select" aria-expanded="false" s